v <- LETTERS[1:10]
matrix <- data.frame(
  x = sample(v, 300, replace = TRUE), 
  y = sample(v, 300, replace = TRUE), 
  z1 = rnorm(300, 10, 1),
  z2 = rnorm(300, 10, 1),
  stringsAsFactors = FALSE
) |> 
  dplyr::group_by(x, y) |> 
  dplyr::summarise(
    z1 = sum(z1),
    z2 = sum(z2)
  ) |>
